{"tid":2382442,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【現形！！】CNBC公然係新聞環節推銷中國製KN95口罩！！！！！！！！","createTime":"2021-01-27T09:38:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T11:43:28.000Z","uid":88743,"like":35,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"91d75f795350ae3e73aa688963f8293921186aac","tid":2382442,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T09:38:23.000Z","msg":"片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/0tkwvs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2F0tkwvs&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdnxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=61d6a61b\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/0tkwvs</a><br />\n<br />\n成個推銷流程係咁：<br />\n<br />\n首先同你講：而家有專家話戴雙重口罩比較好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uJeraem.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuJeraem.jpg&h=c9207098&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y8pVN01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy8pVN01.jpg&h=1f99f42e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拿，靚女主播戴兩隻口罩俾你睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dEeVN01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdEeVN01.jpg&h=a7b23e0f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你睇你睇！研究顯示兩隻口罩可以有更高既Efficiency！！！！三隻仲高！！！！(防止中武肺既efficiency? SORRY唔撚係喎)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8TxXgUm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8TxXgUm.jpg&h=a429d68c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n主播繼續講：拿拿拿，N９５好難買呀，大家千祈唔好用N９５咁高規格呀，應該留返俾有需要既醫護用　(即係話用N９５既都係仆街自私撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LMQND7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLMQND7G.jpg&h=19eac66e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醫護都係用普通口罩咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇下佢地幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />　(唔好俾我係街見到有人用N９5呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eD2TzF1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeD2TzF1.jpg&h=150594a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎啦黎啦<br />\n係枱底拎隻KN９５出黎，同你講：<br />\n其實中國製既KN95好容易就買得到！我係Amazon就買到啦！佢既賣點就係話佢5有層咁多！！！我搭飛機都係用佢架！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有好處就係可以非常之貼面，攝影師！黎！用你個高清鏡頭close up影下個KN９５，係咪好貼面影到我好靚呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xw5BxsG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxw5BxsG.jpg&h=464973c5&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FUgMUF1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFUgMUF1.jpg&h=02a439f0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後加多句：Fit is the Key here<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，最緊要貼面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(暗示：唔想戴兩隻或者三隻咁辛苦，試下戴中國製KN95啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aqi7Ed9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAqi7Ed9.jpg&h=b95e5b42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國口罩有得散貨了<br />\nCNBC做到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4248fc20cd1bc8fa1a6eafcb5ed0dfcf3f93214","tid":2382442,"uid":208511,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T09:46:21.000Z","msg":"又話唔符合歐盟標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"246842e91fed7ca98fe68aa78a97d2fbb6cd1472","tid":2382442,"uid":35296,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T09:49:28.000Z","msg":"Triple Mask 痴撚線公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c028f8f0a966d93ffc6dc306fea916b2eb170b8c","tid":2382442,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T09:50:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac4a78364d2a374edb08ad55340bcb81b778aca","tid":2382442,"uid":88743,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T09:52:22.000Z","msg":"原LINK：<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6Y7nTCavIoA</code></pre><br />\n俾人負皮到仆街<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>Hunter Collins 8 hours ago ：<br />\n&ldquo;The Chinese version kn95&rdquo; 😂 <br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>Jay Abustan Jay Abustan 4 hours ago ：<br />\nI'm also waiting for the Chinese vacci